name: Mister Crybaby Super
details:
Volume/Wah PedalThe Dunlop Mister Crybaby Super Volume/Wah Pedal turns the classic Cry Baby wah into a hot, powered volume pedal in non-wah mode. LED shows you which function is active. The Mister Crybaby pedal uses the Dunlop ECB-003 power supply.
